data.name: label11.Text
data.value:
Most Drag&&Drop implementations in WinForms using preview images struggle with controls that have AllowDrop set to false. While dragging the preview image over such controls, the preview gets hidden, begins to stutter or even freezes while the mouse is moved.
Fluent Drag&&Drop allows you to move preview images over each kind of control or app without getting laggy.

data.name: label15.Text
data.value: The compatibility does not stop with standard WinForms controls but supports Drag&&Drop operations with other applications as well, like the Windows Explorer or any modern web browser. Try it out ...

data.name: label14.Text
data.value: Fluent Drag&&Drop provides an easier and richer experience but uses the same API to implement Drag&&Drop operations as every standard WinForms control. This makes Fluent Drag&&Drop compatible with existing implementations.
